videos.description: Elijah Burns hits the first 3-pointer for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Burns nails triple for Irish

videos.description: T.J. Gibbs makes the jumper through the contact to extend the Fighting Irish lead.
videos.headline: Gibbs finishes tough and-1

videos.description: Bonzie Colson nails the midrange shot to give Notre Dame an 8-point lead at the half.
videos.headline: Colson hits step-back jumper

videos.description: Rex Pflueger sends a nice dish to Martinas Geben, who throws it down.
videos.headline: Geben slams it home for Fighting Irish

videos.description: Bonzie Colson gets his 27th point to go along with 11 rebounds in the game.
videos.headline: Colson knocks down a three
